title: Holly Madison is Down the Rabbit Hole
description: Hold onto your bunny tails, this week on Celebrity Memoir Book Club (@celebritymemoirbookclub) we’re cracking open the dusty old pages of Down the Rabbit Hole by Holly Madison (@hollymadison). Claire (@clairethescare) and Ashley (@ashleyhammm) get a fresh new context on their years of watching the Girls Next Door. Follow us on Instagram @celebritymemoirbookcluband Twitter @cmbc_podcastArt by @adrianne_manpearl !!!! (and theme song by @ashleesimpsonross)Support the show
